# Mission validation state lives here at runtime on Zo.
#
# Subdirectories per milestone (m1, m2, m3, m4, m5, m6) are created by the
# scrutiny-validator and user-testing-validator features auto-injected by the
# mission runner. This .gitkeep exists only so the directory is preserved in
# git on the prep branch; everything else here is created on Zo.
